  "body": "\r\nGood afternoon, everybody,\r\n\r\nI am creating a private ethereum network with the consensus Poa - Proof of Authority (Click) .\r\n\r\nMy Genisis file: https://gist.github.com/Dkdaniz/a995edfc9c5dfc84112c00e876c4bd26\r\n\r\nNumber of Signer: 3\r\n\r\nSigner 1: 0x598BC011b8F50B40a0Ec4CcC6d6E51B785eFB1F7\r\nSigner 2: 0x888d72bA69958860BC67Bd80e90c76D84eE1977a\r\nSigner 3: 0x0639f66b1f77c2f4e5505285f2a1dc93a2f99e1c\r\n\r\nGeth command to rotate the knots:\r\n`\r\ngeth --nousb --datadir=$pwd --syncmode 'full' --port 30310 --miner.gasprice 20000000000 --miner.gastarget 470000000000 --http --http.addr 'localhost' --http.port 8545 --http.api admin,eth,miner,net,txpool,personal,web3 --mine --allow-insecure-unlock --unlock \"**SIGNER-1**\" --password password.txt\r\n`\r\nI have already tested --miner.gasprice for 20000000000, I have tested it with a higher value, I have tested it by removing and leaving it as default.\r\n\r\nMy network has few transfers 10 or 15 per block at most, but it is accepting transactions with zero gasprice.\r\n\r\nHas anyone been through this?\r\n\r\nbecause I would like all transactions to pay a fee, i.e. that GasPrice is different from 0, better, GasPrice > 0;\r\n",
